VIDEO_SESSION
  queue of video sources
  queue of in sessions
  queue of out sessions

  session ID
  input_type: unicast, ASM, SSM
  proc_type: REMAP, PASSTHRU, DATA
  client_mode: BLOCKING, NON_BLOCKING

video source:
  input port
  src IP
  dst IP
  src UDP
  dst UDP
  in_prog_num (-1 for passthru, or not specified)
  alloc_bitrate
  jitter_buffer

in session:
  rid
  QB

out session:
  rid
  qam_id (can derive LC, QB, and channel from this)
  prog num (-1 for passthru)
  alloc_bitrate


-------------------------------------------------------------------------

Usage:

Unicast session (assume no cloning):
  - malloc a VIDEO_SESSION
    - set all the fields

